'''AMD通用封装软件架构'''（{{lang-en|'''AMD Generic Encapsulated Software Architecture'''}}，缩写'''AGESA'''）是[[X86-64|AMD64架构]]（X86-64）的[[主機板|主板]]上初始化系统设备之{{tsl|en|Bootstrap|Bootstrapping|启动}}协议。此类主板的[[BIOS|BIOS]]中之AGESA软件负责[[中央处理器|处理器核心]]、[[内存|内存]]和[[HyperTransport|HyperTransport]]控制器的初始化。

AGESA文档以前只面向签署[[保密协议|保密协议]]（NDA）的AMD合作伙伴提供。2011年初，AGESA开源，以纳入[[coreboot|coreboot]]。<ref name="opensource">{{Cite web|url=http://community.amd.com/community/amd-blogs/business/embedded-systems/blog/2011/02/28/technical-details-on-amd-s-coreboot-source-code-release|title=Technical details on AMD’s coreboot source code release|accessdate=2016-02-01|date=2011-02-28|publisher=[[Advanced_Micro_Devices|AMD]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325040416/http://community.amd.com/community/amd-blogs/amd-business/blog/2011/02/28/technical-details-on-amd-s-coreboot-source-code-release|archivedate=2014-03-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

AGESA隶属{{tsl|en|AMD PowerTune}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://events.ccc.de/congress/2014/Fahrplan/system/attachments/2503/original/ccc-final.pdf|title=AMD x86 SMU firmware analysis|accessdate=2017-04-01|archive-date=2016-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228063050/https://events.ccc.de/congress/2014/Fahrplan/system/attachments/2503/original/ccc-final.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

